Designing Ireland - Series 1, Episode 2




Openness to Influence

As a former colony and island at the edge of Europe, outside influences have always shaped our history, our culture, and our design. Angela and Sandra look at how centuries of migration, invasion and colonisation have resulted in a constant ebb and flow of influence from abroad.




Original Air Date: 12-Nov-2015
